import React from "react";

function Todoform () {
    return (
        <form>
            <label>
                Task:
                <input type="text" name="task" />
             </label>
             <label>
                category:
                <input type="text" name="category" />
             </label>
             <label>
                Due date:
                <input type="date" name="due_date" />
             </label>
        <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
       </form>
    )
}

export default Todoform
